Was a fixed-price currency where bitcoins were be bought and sold.  This was a cash exchange and not an online service. The rates were based on the current BTC/USD market rate from the now defunct [[MtGox]].  The minimum transaction size is R$ 200,00 (duzentos reais). Currencies traded for bitcoins include BRL (Brazilian Real) and USD.  Bitcoins may be sold for either currency as well.

##History

The service was announced on March 31st, 2011 (2.1).

Since 2013 BitcoinToYou are the biggest exchange in Brazil.

